<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11965272-ryan"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1410927451i/11965272._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11965272-ryan">Ryan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    The Temple of the Golden Pavilion follows the story of a young, impressionable priest-in-training Mizoguchi. He is riddled with insecurities due to hi<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    The Temple of the Golden Pavilion follows the story of a young, impressionable priest-in-training Mizoguchi. He is riddled with insecurities due to his stutter and generally views himself as set-apart from the world. He becomes infatuated with beauty, particularly the beauty of the Golden Temple (Kinkaku-ji) which overwhelms him and eventually leads him to burn the Temple down. The drama is in the character development.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
