        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer209851252" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16838913977742331656">Only the Japanese can write books like this, I feel. Lyrically beautiful, aesthetically driven, thoroughly homoerotic, unsettlingly fascist at points, violently modernist, violently anti-modernist, violently violent, operatically melodramatic, sexually repressed, profoundly Buddhist, religious, anti-religious, and set in a landscape of burned temples and told by a misanthropic outsider. Lord I want to go there.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


